# Cursor AI Rules for Tattoo Project

## Context Files
Always include these files when answering questions about deployment, setup, or configuration:
- README.md
- GITHUB_SECRETS_SETUP.md
- REPOSITORIES_SETUP.md
- MIGRATION_GUIDE.md
- docker-compose.prod.yml
- .github/workflows/*.yml

## Project Context
This is a Docker-based tattoo application with automated deployment using:
- GitHub Actions for CI/CD
- Docker Hub for image storage
- DigitalOcean server for hosting
- Prisma for database management

